{"tid":158340,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[請教] ipad 不停咁restart","createTime":"2017-03-16T07:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T04:36:32.000Z","uid":20545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dc72bb15a1af3c7b55a773682743b9c64289728e","tid":158340,"uid":20545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:59:54.000Z","msg":"我部ipad 無用一個星期<br />\n依家諗住用返 按咩制都無反應<br />\n我就以為無電<br />\n一插電 佢就出現白底黑蘋果 過一陣就熄左 跟住又出現白底黑蘋果<br />\n不停咁loop<br />\n可以點做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPS: 試過home + power 去reset 不過都無反應"},{"pid":"724ceb6fd171edee0d474f008da6a5f618b388dd","tid":158340,"uid":37152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:45:12.000Z","msg":"保養已過？<br />\n有冇用iTunes重設"},{"pid":"164644d12b3df689b207dcf6e0ea1d0ba4ffc155","tid":158340,"uid":20545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:41:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>保養已過？<br />\n有冇用iTunes重設</blockquote><br />\n過咗保養<br />\n我依家插落電腦到一啲反應都冇<br />\n做唔到重設<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc0872a9d7672abd056dcdd28ea84667c550673","tid":158340,"uid":6860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:14:24.000Z","msg":"到期了， 插itunes洗機都係咁的話， 底版可能壞了，换啦就出新機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8b868f1167e64d50d9f64a2b9a2b06b8175ff9","tid":158340,"uid":20545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T23:33:55.000Z","msg":"我用風筒吹下佢<br />\n就無事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09360103a916136ffa29190ee13fe54de51c7f3","tid":158340,"uid":66723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T23:53:18.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪用其他嘢叉電?<br />\n之前試過,最後發現係部電腦/火牛唔夠V數<br />\n佢開機嗰下用嘅電多過叉嘅電,所以熄左<br />\n用返原裝ipad火牛就開到"},{"pid":"b4e284cdd301bcf43d7b323353b13ea1712f1d59","tid":158340,"uid":20545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T04:36:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係咪用其他嘢叉電?<br />\n之前試過,最後發現係部電腦/火牛唔夠V數<br />\n佢開機嗰下用嘅電多過叉嘅電,所以熄左<br />\n用返原裝ipad火牛就開到</blockquote><br />\n我用原裝ipad牛<br />\n我都唔知點解用風筒吹就得<br />\n可能潮濕天氣有關"}]}